if u have morpascape click on help then click on item ID the u will see load of item names. then try search for dragon
then u should see loads of dragon items and an ID near it. then exit the Item ID list. after u done that u gotta type
::pickup (e.g if u want 9999999 coins and the ID is 0995 type ::pickup 0995 9999999 to get 9999999 coins) DO IT AS MANY TIMES U LIKE
